---
title: Nan's Chicken & Garlicky Roasted Veggies with Hollandaise
description: Chicken and veggies is a simple weekday meal that never fails to please. How about we spice things up a bit tonight?
Why not try roasting the chicken with our Nan’s special seasoning or sprinkling a Tuscan herb seasoning over a colourful
serving of veggies so when they roast all those flavours will be locked in. A simple dish with a fantastic twist.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
